dct_title_s: Upper Saranac Lake, New York, Franklin County / produced by the United States Geological Survey.
dct_description_sm: Folded title: 1:25,000-scale metric topographic map of Upper Saranac Lake, New York showing contours and elevations in meters, highways, roads and other manmade structures, water features, woodland areas, geographic names. "Projection and 1000-meter grid, zone 18: universal transverse Mercator." Relief shown by contours at 5-meter intervals and spot heights. Depth shown by soundings. "4474-131-T25." Includes location map, metric conversion table and index to adjoining sheets.
dct_publisher_sm: Reston, VA : United States Geological Survey, 1979.
